{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/keep-sticky-header-visible-after-scrolling","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1667,"date":"2022-06-27T06:56:18","date_gmt":"2022-06-27T06:56:18","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1667"},"modified":"2022-06-27T07:32:05","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T07:32:05","slug":"keep-sticky-header-visible-after-scrolling","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/keep-sticky-header-visible-after-scrolling/","title":{"rendered":"Dawn theme: keep sticky header visible after scrolling"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Have you ever wanted to show your Dawn theme&#8217;s banner image below a transparent header? Or maybe simply keep your sticky header permanently sticky, even after scrolling down?<br><br>If so, this is the right tutorial for you. I&#8217;ll be guiding you on how to add a beautiful, performative and thoroughly tested &#8220;permanently sticky&#8221; header for the Dawn theme, one that also works on other pages without adding weird margins. All it takes is pasting one single piece of code. <br><br><a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview of how the final result will look like.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-the-theme\">Adding the code to the theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to Online Store > Themes > Actions > Edit Code.</li><li>Search for this file:<br><br>header.liquid<br></li><li>press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for exactly this:<br><br><strong>{% schema</strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"927\" height=\"600\" class=\"wp-image-1683\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d1.jpg 927w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d1-850x550.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d1-768x497.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 927px) 100vw, 927px\" /></li><li>Now, delete everything <strong>below </strong>the {% schema %} line, including the {% schema %}.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1134\" height=\"730\" class=\"wp-image-1570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg 1134w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-850x547.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1134px) 100vw, 1134px\" /><br><br>5. Copy all of the following code and paste it at the very bottom of the file and save.<br><br>[gist]443cf7cd02dc34e081500c71217c7566[gist]</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-customizing-the-sticky-header-options\">Customizing the sticky header options</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Still on the page that you are, at the top, click on &#8220;customize theme&#8221;. </li><li>On the left, inside the Header section, you&#8217;ll find new options to customize your header. <br><br>You can change the colors, spacing and a few other settings as you please!</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-1 wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in:<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Arrows &amp; vertical thumbnails for Dawn&#8217;s product pages<span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/w4LaQF8cp1akInO4Cp/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-fix-zoom-images-size-mobile-desktop\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Dawn lightbox: responsive images, slider and arrows <span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media4.giphy.com/media/aBmvXTlfvHiPMXtx4a/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Prevent your theme&#8217;s sticky header from disappearing when you scroll down.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1691,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[435],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/sticky_header-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/sticky_header-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/sticky_header-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Dawn Theme"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1667"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp